videos.headline: Idaho's Henderson muscles his way into the end zone
videos.description: D.J. Henderson pounds his way in for the touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Ray keeps it himself for the TD
videos.description: Rajun Cajuns quarterback Dion Ray takes the keeper 3  yards to even the score in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Louisiana's Ragas bulls his way for TD

videos.headline: Nunez throws 45-yard TD pass
